    <item>
      <title>南非考虑收紧场外衍生品规则</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/south-africa-mulls-tightening-over-the-counter-derivative-rules</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非即将出台期待已久的金融规则改革，并已指定对场外衍生品和非上市金融市场活动进行更严格的审查。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/south-africa-mulls-tightening-over-the-counter-derivative-rules</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:01:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>大选临近，美国债务出售计划具有政治敏感性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/us-debt-sale-plan-gets-politically-sensitive-with-election-ahead</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部更新债券销售计划是债券交易商每季度的标志性事件，但在拜登政府被一些共和党人指责操纵发行策略后，该计划现在也具有政治敏感性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-29/us-debt-sale-plan-gets-politically-sensitive-with-election-ahead</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Jul 2024 10:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
